Contract CO: searchForConnections

Operation: searchForConnections(dep_station, arr_station)
Cross References: System sequence diagram 1

Preconditions:
• User enters valid station names

Postconditions: 
• A list of connections (either direct or indirect) appear on screen
• User can see connection(s) information: cost(first & second class), duration, departure & arrival times
• The connection(s) start from dep_station and arrive to arr_station with no more than 2 stops linking them
• The connection after a stop does not leave before the connection before the same stop arrives at the station